# Sports edge strengthening roadmap

Cheapest-first. Do not skip phases or jump to ML/news scraping.

## Phase 1 — Bet assessment (annotate only)
`sports_bet_assessment.py`: edge tier, match quality, partition coherence, liquidity sanity.
Attach `bet_assessment` to every opportunity; **do not block live** yet.

## Phase 2 — Multi-book consensus
Require 2+ sharp books within ~2¢ of fair before live fire.

## Phase 3 — Sport-specific gates (paper-learned)
After ~30–50 legs/sport: ban losing price buckets; FIFA tie edge floor; tennis title match; MLB T-2h gate.

## Phase 4 — Execution quality
Live book before order; IOC when edge fat; passive only when edge ≥8¢+.

## Do NOT do first
Custom per-sport ML, injury/news scraping, bigger stakes before Phase 1 paper CLV.
